{
  "stem": "19218.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We'd do everything else that has to be done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But he's the cook to cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he opened up the jar of peanut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I presume it was good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And he told us, this is not for you guys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It's no good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Don't you even touch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Don't even think of touching it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And of course, a day later, it was empty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And he had a good time just eating the peanut there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the guy brought us some canned-- canned, I think it was, gefilte fish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And he took some pictures of us also at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And suddenly, the-- the Germans decided to make a stand in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And there was fighting going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I thought it was going on for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But I could have been wrong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But I thought there was-- we were right on the front lines in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I believe this city was called Dessau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "It was someplace around Dessau where they've done this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And this is this-- now after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And we saw those truckloads of killed soldiers being brought back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they have also-- we were right with the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "You know, being hungry all your life-- for the-- for the last three, four years, that we were where the kitchen was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Because the kitchen always had enough food to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And this is the only thing which we cared about, is food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were eating with the-- the guys on the front lines that they had all the other goodies out, cigarettes, as many as they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because those are the guys who went back to the front lines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember in one incident, a dessert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, we all had dessert, too, they gave us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was pineapple.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
